        {
            "id": 6009445,
            "title": "外資近5日賣超個股",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計賣超 5 日的股票<br/>國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)、陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計賣超 4 日的股票<br/>國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW<